Media
Novels
Hana Oni is written by Risa. It was originally serialized on the original fiction website,  "The Little Window in the Little Room"}}, since 2004. It later received a print publication by  under the Regalo imprint, with illustrations provided by  from Design Factory. In 2017, Kodansha re-released the series in  format under the Kodansha Bunko imprint.
